 {"id":"br-r37-c1-j6qpf","title":"parity: draw_bipartite signature divergence — fnx requires top_nodes positionally, nx accepts only **kwargs","description":"fnx.draw_bipartite has signature (G, top_nodes, pos=None, **kwds) where top_nodes is a required positional arg, but networkx.drawing.nx_pylab.draw_bipartite has (G, **kwargs). Drop-in calls like nx.draw_bipartite(G) work in nx but fnx raises TypeError missing positional argument top_nodes. Fix: align signature to (G, **kwargs) and pull top_nodes out of kwargs (or compute it via bipartite_sets if absent), so fnx accepts the same call shape as nx.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-26T04:28:46.975023293Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-26T04:49:45.891385685Z","closed_at":"2026-04-26T04:49:45.889512479Z","close_reason":"Shipped in 097c007: draw_bipartite now (G, **kwargs) matching nx; top_nodes pulled from kwargs and inferred via bipartite_sets if absent. 170 smoke tests pass.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"br-r37-c1-jk4ym","title":"trophic_levels raises on empty graph but test_empty_graph expects {}","description":"fnx.trophic_levels delegates to nx for all inputs after the directed check. nx raises NetworkXError('This graph has no basal nodes') on empty input. But the existing test_trophic_parity.py::TestTrophicLevels::test_empty_graph asserts fnx.trophic_levels(empty_DG) == {} — the project's intent is to be more permissive than nx on this edge case (empty graph trivially has no trophic levels to compute, returning empty dict is user-friendly).

Repro:
  fnx.trophic_levels(fnx.DiGraph()) -> NetworkXError (delegates to nx)
  Test expects: == {}

Pre-existing test failure. Fix: short-circuit empty-graph case to return {} before delegation. Companion functions trophic_differences / trophic_incoherence_parameter should be similarly examined.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-26T19:42:48.595532752Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-26T19:45:25.886513669Z","closed_at":"2026-04-26T19:45:25.884361404Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
